data.description: Great 2 story home in popular Langston  Hughes Elementary area w/primary plus 2 addtl beds up -- 4th bed in the finished bsmt. Seller has installed new floors thruout the 1st level! Kitchen has granite countertops, an island plus nice eat-in area. SS appliances; gas stove! Frig, washer & dryer can stay with the home. Walk in pantry! Formal dining or office -- you choose. Living rm has cozy corner fireplace & lots of windows for natural light!  On 2nd level you will find the extra large primary suite w/oversized shower, jetted  tub, double sinks & HUGE primary closet. Bsmt features family rm, 4th bdrm, game area & storage rm.  Large fenced backyard w/storage shed. Close to shopping, restaurants, Rock Chalk Park & easy access to K-10/I-70.  Call to see today!!!
